'main' seeds random function

initial loop is called:
	screen is cleared
	user asked to input choice
	returns a value

gen_random_word is called:
	a nullptr is initialised
	a random word is chosen from dictionary
	string is allocated to be the size of word
	string is set to be the word + returned

main_loop is called using word + word_size:
	string 'guess' of size 'word_size' is declared
	input is taken from user and stored in guess
	respective value is returned if guess is correct
